\v 12 Tsen³ ma³-na³ nca³ nˀion¹ tˀa³con³ ntsˀe³ Silvano, je² xi³ qui³squi³ xi³ tˀa³tsˀan⁴, nca³ an³ qui³sca³ni³ i⁴tse¹-no³ en¹. Ti²vˀe³ne²³-no³, ti²si³qui²xi⁴ya³-no³ nca³ ña³qui³ cjoa⁴nta³-le⁴ Ni³na¹ je²-vi⁴ xi³ ti³yo³jin³-lao⁴³.  
\v 13 Si¹ti²ˀnta³-no³ je² cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴ Cristo xi³ tjio¹ ya⁴ Babilonia, xi³ to⁴jnco³ qui³tjoe¹jin³ cao⁴ jon². Si¹ti²ˀnta³-no³ Marcos, ˀnti¹-na⁴.  
\v 14 Ti⁴ti²ˀntao³ xi²nquio⁴³, tˀe²tˀa³tsˀoao²³ xi²nquio⁴³, nca³ cˀoa⁴-sˀin² tsjoa³chao³ xi²nquio⁴³. Ca²ta³njen³nchˀan¹jin³ ni⁴ma⁴-no³ nca³tsˀio³ xi³ ti³yo³cao⁴³ Jesucristo. Cˀoa⁴ ca²ta³ma³.